GnUser

public GnUser(IGnUserStore userStore,
              java.lang.String clientId,
              java.lang.String clientTag,
              java.lang.String applicationVersion)
       throws GnException
Create a GnUser with the provided Client ID and Client Tag. Check user storage for an existing user and if found reconstitutes the user. Reconstitution does not count towards the user count for your client in Gracenote Service. If not found in user storage a new user is created.

Parameters:
userStore - [in] User store delegate
clientId - [in] Client Identifer
clientTag - [in] Client Tag
applicationVersion - [in] Application version
Throws:
GnException
